patthana16.10:1.1_0: Abyākataṁ rūpiṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca nakusalo narūpī dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana16.10:1.1_1: Abyākataṁ rūpiṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca naakusalo narūpī dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana16.10:1.1_2: Abyākataṁ rūpiṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca nakusalo narūpī ca naakusalo narūpī ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā.
